bashrc -Sets the prompt using colors as well as send escape codes to screen using the PROMPT_COMMAND.
        Sends a screen hardstatus string in order to display current user/host info.
        Sets the screen window title to the highest level of the PWD when at a prompt but displays the current running command when entered.

screenrc -Formats a hardstatus bar to display open windows and their pwd/running process as well as the hardstatus setting.